dialogStrings:
“Well, well. Long time no see.
What have you been up to?
Let's see…what was your name?”

“No, Gramps!
This isn't anyone you know!
This is just some stranger who
barged into our house!”

“Oh, how exciting.
You a friend of my grandson's?”

“No, Gramps!
These guy's are creepy!
They're runnin' all over the place!”

“Oh, you know lately things have been like that.
You can even see the moon at noon.
Everyone's celebrating.”

“No, Gramps!
That's a big red planet in the sky!
Everyone's scared of it!!”

“What are we going to do, Gramps?
Some strange-looking girl came in here
a minute ago and I…”

“Oh no!
More weirdos!”{PAUSE}“No, these aren't like the one
from a while ago,
but these ones look weird, too!”
